储层性能问题是系统故障的源头，通过调用链向上传播导致cartservice和checkoutservice的连锁延迟。虽然adservice-2存在应用层问题，但不是本次系统级性能故障的主要根因。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nDISAGREED", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "consensus_decision": "AGREED", "current_hypothesis": "redis-cart-0 is the root cause due to storage layer performance degradation causing cascading failures in cartservice and upstream services", "current_task_instruction": "当前处于【分析阶段】。\n以下是你可以访问的全量上下文信息，包含了用户输入、当前假设、以及其他所有智能体的历史发现：\n================================\nUUID: 6a643823-196\n\nUser Query: Determine the root cause of the system fault during 2025-06-10T15:11:01Z to 2025-06-10T15:21:01Z.\n\n\n[RAW DATA CONTEXT]\n\n--- Raw Log Data ---\n{'status': 'success', 'message': '成功加载日志数据。UUID: 6a643823-196，共 6 条错误日志', 'filtered_logs': 'node_name,service_name,pod_name,message,occurrence_count\\naiops-k8s-08,adservice,adservice-2,\"Exception in thread \"\"Attach Listener\"\" java.lang.reflect.InvocationTargetException\",出现次数:2\\naiops-k8s-08,adservice,adservice-2,Agent failed to start!,出现次数:2\\naiops-k8s-08,adservice,adservice-2,Caused by: java.lang.Exception: Main : attempting to load Byteman agent more than once,出现次数:2\\naiops-k8s-08,adservice,adservice-2,org.jboss.byteman.agent.Transformer : possible trigger for rule AdService-getRandomAds-latency-1749568261 in class hipstershop.AdService,出现次数:1\\naiops-k8s-08,adservice,adservice-2,RuleTriggerMethodAdapter.injectTriggerPoint : inserting trigger into hipstershop.AdService.getRandomAds() java.util.List for rule AdService-getRandomAds-latency-1749568261,出现次数:1\\naiops-k8s-08,adservice,adservice-2,org.jboss.byteman.agent.Transformer : inserted trigger for AdService-getRandomAds-latency-1749568261 in class hipstershop.AdService,出现次数:1\\n', 'unique_entities': {'pod_name': ['adservice-2'], 'service_name': ['adservice'], 'node_name': ['aiops-k8s-08']}, 'matched_anomaly': 'Determine the root cause o